    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1901-12-18T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1901-12-18T00:00:00-05:00" n="689"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d689">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Swenson</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Copenhagen</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-12-18">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 18, 1901</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Minister for Foreign Affairs says the treaty must be laid before the King and the
                    Folkething Committee on Finance before signed, which will require a few days.
                    The Rigsdag proposes plebiscite, independent of treaty, if necessary. Minister
                    for Foreign Affairs may yield.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Swenson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
